OL,3,CPolice Cadets sleep rough for charity
OL,5,FBlackpool and Fylde Police Cadets have
OL,6,Ftaken on their latest and most
OL,7,Fgruelling challenge, a 16-hour 'Rough
OL,8,FSleep' event for the charity Helping
OL,9,FHearts Fylde.
OL,11,FThe group of cadets, aged 13-18, spent
OL,12,Fthe night sleeping outdoors in a car
OL,13,Fpark in Blackpool from sunset on
OL,14,FDecember 20th to sunrise on December
OL,15,F21st.
OL,17,FThis period, classed as the longest
OL,18,Fnight leading up to the Winter
OL,19,FSolstice, offered a stark glimpse into
OL,20,Fthe conditions faced by the homeless
OL,21,Fcommunity the charity supports.
