OL,3,CPolice Cadets sleep rough for charity
OL,5,FWith low temperatures and wind, it
OL,6,Ffelt like -1 degrees outside.
OL,8,FThe cadets first connected with
OL,9,FHelping Hearts Fylde last year, with
OL,10,Fmany senior members volunteering at
OL,11,Fthe charity's weekly soup kitchen.
OL,13,FFounded in 2020, Helping Hearts Fylde
OL,14,Fsupports the entire Fylde Coast
OL,15,Fcommunity. The charity has reported a
OL,16,Fdrastic increase in demand for its
OL,17,Fservices, stating that the number of
OL,18,Fpeople who rely on them has grown by
OL,19,Fover 800% due to the current cost-of-
OL,20,Fliving crisis.
