OL,3,CPolice Cadets sleep rough for charity
OL,5,FHelping Hearts is a wholly volunteer-
OL,6,Fled team, relying on kind donations to
OL,7,Fcontinue its vital work. They provide
OL,8,Fa comprehensive range of support,
OL,9,Fincluding a food and baby bank, as
OL,10,Fwell as additional services.
OL,12,FThe cadets undertook the challenge
OL,13,Fspecifically to raise awareness and
OL,14,Fcritical funding for local families
OL,15,Fand individuals in need across the
OL,16,FFylde Coast.
